desc: Pretty Mama WaistBeads is a jewelry brand that was created with the intent to promote self love and self awareness. Handmade waist-beads, anklets and more highlight our most shapely areas with crystals, gold, charms and gemstones. We have the perfect adornments for all of our Pretty Mamas of any size or shape.

layout.text: Support us for free just by taking a selfie 😘
